Seagate Acquisition of Samsung Hard-Disk Unit Approved by EU

-- B y   A o i f e   W h i t e
-- 
2011-10-19T09:15:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/seagate-acquisition-of-samsung-hard-disk-unit-approved-by-eu.html
Seagate Technology Plc (STX)  won European
Union approval to buy  Samsung Electronics Co Ltd (005930) ’s unprofitable
hard-disk storage unit as shrinking sales accelerates
consolidation in the industry.  The European Commission said in a statement today that the
deal won’t “significantly impede effective competition” in the
region.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aoife White in Brussels at 
